OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1771927474
OL,3,CTwo men jailed for 'disturbing'
OL,4,Ckilling of sheep
OL,6,FTwo men have been sent to jail for the
OL,7,F"disturbing" killing of a sheep on the
OL,8,FSouth Downs in 2023.
OL,10,FLeighton Ashby, 22, and Oakley
OL,11,FHollands, 20, appeared at Lewes Crown
OL,12,FCourt on Monday (23 February)
OL,13,Ffollowing a "catastrophic" attack on
OL,14,Flivestock near Ditchling Beacon.
OL,16,FThe court heard that on the evening of
OL,17,FThursday, 2 November 2023, the pair
OL,18,Fdrove to a field where they began
OL,19,Fchasing a flock of sheep.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
